BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313439657@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T014016Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T183000
SUMMARY:Candlelight Yoga @ Hotel Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Nourish 108 Ayurveda & Yoga\nJoin me for 60 minutes of nourishing de-stress yoga by candlelight in the Brooklyn Ballroom (upstairs) at Hotel Petaluma. Please bring your own mat and any props you might need (block\, strap\, bolster strap\, blanket)\, and arrive a few minutes early to get situated.\n\nAll levels welcome!\n\nDrop in is $18\, class passes are available. FREE for hotel guests.\nSign up through the calendar at [www.nourish108.com/classes](www.nourish108.com/classes) or at the front desk if you're a guest. Credit/debit in advance\, cash/Venmo on site.\n\nI look forward to practicing with you!рЯІШрЯПївАНвЩАпЄПрЯХѓпЄП
